cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper deals with the application of deep reinforcement learning (DRL) to car-following control, specifically Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC), with consideration of vehicle dynamics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper focuses on the application of DRL. The second most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics), as the paper deals with control of autonomous vehicles. The third likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), as the paper deals with the application of AI techniques to control problems. The fourth likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), as the paper deals with control of a dynamic system. The fifth likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), as the paper deals with perception and control of a physical system.
